title: Inttelligent
subTitle: A successful software engineer becomes a vigilante following the demise of his mentor in a bid to seek revenge against those responsible for the latter's death.

title: Return of Hanuman
subTitle: Lord Hanuman reincarnates as Maruti to help Minku, a bullied boy, while addressing challenges of modern life, courage and the importance of protecting nature.

title: Paheli
subTitle: A ghost falls in love with a newly-wed woman and disguises himself as her husband when her spouse goes away for business.

title: Filler
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Hunterrr
subTitle: Mandar is a self-confessed sex addict who is only interested in sex and holds no regards for love or feelings. However, his life changes when he meets Tripti and wishes to settle down with her.

title: Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro
subTitle: Two photographers, who are employed by a newspaper editor to expose the scandalous activities of the rich, come across corruption by a builder and accidentally photograph a murder.

title: Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Vishal In Laatti Charge
subTitle: A police constable lands in grave danger when he gets trapped by a dangerous gang in a building with his sick son. He must strive to defeat the villains and escape to safety.

title: Sita Ram
subTitle: Ram, a young boy, lives in a monastery waiting for Sita to return and take care of him. However, Sita returns, years later, but with an ulterior motive.

title: Yodha
subTitle: After he fails to save a hijacked flight, Arun, a soldier, is suspended. When he is found onboard another hijacked flight, his intentions are questioned.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: Seenu, a criminal, escapes from the prison and places his doppelganger, Shankar, in his place. However, upon learning about Shankar's noble mission, he takes up the cause himself.

title: Khaidi No. 150

title: Raaz Rangon Ka
subTitle: A teacher, smitten student and struggling filmmaker become entangled in the search for a missing teen. Their quest reveals hidden truths that threaten to upend lives.

title: Sharafat Gayi Tel Lene
subTitle: When an ordinary man discovers crores in his account, he is thrown into a tangled mess of crime, impersonation and corrupt connections he never asked for.

title: Chaalis Chauraasi
subTitle: Four friends hatch a scheme to steal money by impersonating the police. However, on their way, they run into a real inspector who enlists them to carry out an encounter.

title: Damayanthi
subTitle: A young man struggles to pay off his father's debts and decides to visit his family's abandoned bungalow. However, he soon realises that it is haunted by a vengeful ghost.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

title: Aakhri Yudh
subTitle: Babji, a loan recovery agent, decides to help Kavya when he finds her being chased by her family. However, Kavya's brother thinks that Babji and her sister are lovers and attacks his family.

title: Ram Setu
subTitle: Aryan, an archaeologist, is an atheist and publishes a controversial report on Rama Setu. Things take a turn when he sets out to prove its existence and becomes a believer in the process.

title: Hungama
subTitle: A millionaire businessman living in a village decides to move to the city with his wife. However, things take a comical turn as a case of mistaken identity causes chaos in their lives.

title: Happy New Year
subTitle: Shuffling between old grudges and new grooves, Charlie and his friends bumble their way through an international dance competition to break into a heavily guarded vault of diamonds.

title: Bholaa Shankar
subTitle: A cab driver in Calcutta struggles to rebuild his life with his sister while confronting a haunting past. Subsequently, he fights to protect his future and family from the city's gritty underworld.

title: The Return of Abhimanyu
subTitle: A military officer borrows money from a bank using fake papers for his sister's marriage. However, when the money goes missing from his account, he begins an investigation that leads him to a hacker.

title: The Return of Abhimanyu

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Global Baba
subTitle: Pehlwaan, a criminal, narrowly escapes a police encounter and uses a holy man's guise to hide. Though he soon amasses a large number of followers, he continues to carry out his illegal activities.

title: Jigarbaaz Khiladi
subTitle: Shiva arrives in Chennai from Canada and starts up a real estate business. However, things take a turn when he realises that he is being cheated by the people he trusts.

title: Karkash
subTitle: A wayward husband vows to punish his dutiful wife after a false rumour spreads in society that questions her fidelity. Eventually, the woman must take dire measures to prove her loyalty and honour.

title: Yuvaraj
subTitle: Yuva enrols in an engineering college after getting banned from his sport and picks up fights with local students. However, his life gets more strained when his father flees, owing a huge debt.

title: Conjuring Kannappan
subTitle: When a man plucks a feather off a dreamcatcher, he has nightmares where injuries reflect in the real world. But when this affects his family and friends, they decide to find the root of the problem.

title: Express Khiladi
subTitle: A pantry worker and a make-up artist develop a romance aboard a runaway train, where they must confront dangerous challenges to save themselves and others.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Pichaikkaran
subTitle: A rich businessman and a poor beggar's lives intersect, showing how money influences their fates as one fights off greedy predators and the other searches for his long-lost sister.

title: Rajini The Jailer
subTitle: A retired jailer lives a peaceful life with his family. But when his son, who is a policeman, goes missing and is supposedly killed, he is forced to go back to his world of crime and find the killer.

title: Petta
subTitle: In a bid to save his best friend's son Anwar, hostel warden Kaali goes against local goons. However, everything goes haywire when he is forced to face his past.
